  "description": "<p><em>We sang about the sun and danced among the trees And we listened to the whispers of the city on the breeze - Ancient pre-Cataclysm proverb</em></p><p>A set of oracle arrays for cities and districts for the Ironsworn: Starforged rpg. When determining the features of a settlement district, use these oracle arrays for inspiration.</p><p>The oracle arrays use the following oracles:</p><p>AR - <a href=\"https://p-d-gallagher.itch.io/augmented-reality\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">Augmented Reality The Holistic City Kit</a> by <a href=\"https://itch.io/profile/p-d-gallagher\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">Geist Hack Games</a></p><p>IC - <a href=\"https://vishae.itch.io/ironcity-district-generator\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">Iron City District Generator</a> by <a href=\"https://vishae.itch.io/\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">vishae</a></p><p>SEO – <a href=\"https://preview.drivethrurpg.com/en/product/417619/Starsmith-Expanded-Oracles\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">Starsmith: Expanded Oracles&gt; by </a><a href=\"https://preview.drivethrurpg.com/en/publisher/8584/eric-bright\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">Eric Bright</a></p><p>CP - <a href=\"https://jendave.itch.io/i-owe-my-soul-to-the-company-planet\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">I Owe My Soul to the Company Planet</a> by <a href=\"https://jendave.itch.io/\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">David Hudson</a></p>",
